								<header class="major">
									<h2>Brief Bio</h2>
									<p> I joined MIT Department of Physics as a graduate student in 2014. I moved to Princeton Univerity as a visiting student in 2017 with my advisor <a href="https://scholar.princeton.edu/jwinn/home">Josh Winn </a>. I spend most of my time at Princeton nowadays. Previously, I received B.A. in Natural Science and M.Sci in Physics from University of Cambridge in 2014 with First Class Honours.</p>
